OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773133490
OL,3,CNew footage suggests US may be
OL,4,Cresponsible for Iran school attack
OL,6,FNew footage appears to show a US
OL,7,Fmissile may have been responsible for
OL,8,Fthe airstrike on an Iranian school on
OL,9,FFebruary 28.
OL,11,FIt directly contradicts the suggestion
OL,12,Fby US President Donald Trump that Iran
OL,13,Fwas responsible for the hit, which
OL,14,Fkilled at least 165 people at the
OL,15,Fstart of the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
