OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773133490
OL,3,CNew footage suggests US may be
OL,4,Cresponsible for Iran school attack
OL,6,FThe new footage, first analysed by the
OL,7,Finvestigative group Bellingcat, was
OL,8,Ftaken the day the Shajareh Tayyiba
OL,9,Fschool was struck but was circulated
OL,10,Fon Sunday by Iran's semi-official Mehr
OL,11,Fnews agency.
OL,13,FIt appears to show a US missile
OL,14,Ftargeting the Islamic Revolutionary
OL,15,FGuard Corps (IRGC) naval base adjacent
OL,16,Fto the school.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773133490
OL,3,CNew footage suggests US may be
OL,4,Cresponsible for Iran school attack
OL,6,FThe video shows a munition consistent
OL,7,Fwith an American BGM or UGM-109
OL,8,FTomahawk Land Attack Missile (TLAM)
OL,9,Fstriking a location inside the IRGC
OL,10,Fbase, according to reports by ITV
OL,11,FNews' US partner CNN.
OL,13,FTrevor Ball, a Bellingcat researcher,
OL,14,Fidentified the munition as a Tomahawk
OL,15,Fcruise missile, and the US is the only
OL,16,Fparticipant in the war known to
OL,17,Fpossess that particular weapon it is
OL,18,Fthe first evidence of a munition used
OL,19,Fin the strike
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
