PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773133490
OL,3,CNew footage suggests US may be
OL,4,Cresponsible for Iran school attack
OL,6,FAs the camera pans to the right, smoke
OL,7,Fcan be seen from the direction of the
OL,8,Fschool, according to Iranian state
OL,9,Fmedia.
OL,11,FIt appears to have been filmed from a
OL,12,Fnearby construction site on February
OL,13,F28, in Minab, southern Iran.
OL,15,FEvidence compiled by CNN and analysed
OL,16,Fby experts had already suggested that
OL,17,Fthe US was responsible for the
OL,18,Fincident, but Trump said on Saturday
OL,19,Fthat was not the case.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
