OL,3,CNew footage suggests US may be
OL,4,Cresponsible for Iran school attack
OL,6,F"Based on what I've seen, that was
OL,7,Fdone by Iran," Trump told reporters,
OL,8,Fas he said Iranian munitions were
OL,9,F"very inaccurate".
OL,11,FUS Defence Secretary Pete Hegseth was
OL,12,Fmore cautious in attributing blame,
OL,13,Fwhen he was asked about the strike:
OL,14,F"We're certainly investigating, but
OL,15,Fthe only side that targets civilians
OL,16,Fis Iran."
