OL,3,CNew footage suggests US may be
OL,4,Cresponsible for Iran school attack
OL,6,FBellingcat said the footage "appears
OL,7,Fto contradict" Trump's claim.
OL,9,FNeither the US military's Central
OL,10,FCommand nor the Israeli military have
OL,11,Fso far commented on the new video.
