PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773133490
OL,3,CNew footage suggests US may be
OL,4,Cresponsible for Iran school attack
OL,6,FCNN reported on Friday that satellite
OL,7,Fimagery, geolocated videos, public
OL,8,Fstatements from US officials and the
OL,9,Fassessment of munitions experts
OL,10,Fsuggested that the Shajare Tayyiba
OL,11,Felementary school in Minab was hit on
OL,12,FFebruary 28 at around the same time as
OL,13,Fan attack that American forces likely
OL,14,Fcarried out on a neighbouring IRGC
OL,15,Fnaval base.
OL,17,FThe US is the only country
OL,18,Fparticipating in the current conflict
OL,19,Fknown to have Tomahawk missiles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
