PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773133490
OL,3,CNew footage suggests US may be
OL,4,Cresponsible for Iran school attack
OL,6,FJanina Dill, an expert on
OL,7,Finternational law at Oxford
OL,8,FUniversity, wrote on X that even if
OL,9,Fthe strike was a misidentification -
OL,10,Fand the attacker believed that the
OL,11,Fschool had been a part of the
OL,12,Fneighbouring IRGC base - it would
OL,13,Fstill be "a very serious violation of
OL,14,Finternational law".
OL,16,F"Attackers are under an obligation to
OL,17,Fdo everything feasible to verify the
OL,18,Fstatus of targeted object," she said.
